.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Logo-Cafe-de-lOpera.png\" alt=\"Cafe de l\u2019Opera at Caravelle Saigon 5 Star Hotel, Vietnam\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-47qo8jvr fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">SPRING TAPAS<\/h2>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-47qo8jvs fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">A journey to delight your sense!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Celebrate Spring Festival with a wide selection of tapas feasts is a perfect way to treat those you hold near and dear!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Our Chef has created a unique selection of Tapas Menu with a bold combination of cherries and peanuts. Beautifully presented in bite-sized portions, our Tapas menu allows for greater choice and variety in a meal. Yet, don&rsquo;t forget to treat yourself to a glass of cocktail for the most glamourous experience, in the most elegant environment.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Offer:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Tapas menu is proposed from VND 189,000 ++ per portion<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* VND 270,000++ for a glass of cocktail by Singleton<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-5jeu7toj fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Price is subject to 5% Service Charge &amp; 8% VAT<\/em><br \/><em>For more information, please call (84) 2838 234 999 or email: culinary@caravellehotel.com<\/em><\/p>\n<p><\/div><section class=\"ffb-id-5s2km83q fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--2 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-5s2km83r fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-5s2km83t fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/spring-tapas-footer.jpg\" alt=\"Spring-tapas\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-